methods.fillChunk:
Lookup each element in a RowSequence and write the result to a WritableLongChunk.

:param fillContext: (io.deephaven.engine.table.ChunkSource.FillContext) - The FillContext
:param innerRowKeys: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableLongChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.engine.rowset.chunkattributes.RowKeys>) - The result chunk
:param outerRowKeys: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSequence) - The row keys to lookup in this RowRedirection
methods.fillPrevChunk:
Lookup each element in a RowSequence and write the result to a WritableLongChunk, using previous
 values.

:param fillContext: (io.deephaven.engine.table.ChunkSource.FillContext) - The FillContext
:param innerRowKeys: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableLongChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.engine.rowset.chunkattributes.RowKeys>) - The result chunk
:param outerRowKeys: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSequence) - The row keys to lookup in this RowRedirection
methods.get:
Simple redirected lookup.

:param outerRowKey: (long) - The "outer" row key
:return: (long) The corresponding "inner" row key, or RowSequence.NULL_ROW_KEY if no mapping exists
methods.getPrev:
Simple redirected lookup, using previous values.

:param outerRowKey: (long) - The "outer" row key
:return: (long) The corresponding "inner" row key, or RowSequence.NULL_ROW_KEY if no mapping exists
methods.makeFillContext:
Make a FillContext for this RowRedirection. The default implementation supplied RowRedirection.DEFAULT_FILL_INSTANCE,
 suitable for use with the default implementation of
 RowRedirection.fillChunk(ChunkSource.FillContext, WritableLongChunk, RowSequence),
 RowRedirection.fillChunkUnordered(ChunkSource.FillContext, WritableLongChunk, LongChunk), and
 RowRedirection.fillPrevChunk(ChunkSource.FillContext, WritableLongChunk, RowSequence).

:param chunkSize: (int) - The maximum number of mappings that will be retrieved in one operation
:param sharedContext: (io.deephaven.engine.table.SharedContext) - A SharedContext for use when the same RowRedirection will be used with the same
        keysToMap by multiple consumers
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.ChunkSource.FillContext) The FillContext to use
methods.put:
Add or change a mapping from outerRowKey to innerRowKey.

:param outerRowKey: (long) - The outer row key to map from
:param innerRowKey: (long) - The inner row key to map to
:return: (long) The inner row key previously mapped from outerRowKey, or RowSequence.NULL_ROW_KEY if there was
         no mapping
methods.putVoid:
Like WritableRowRedirection.put(long, long), but without requiring the implementation to provide a return value. May be more
 efficient in some cases.

:param outerRowKey: (long) - The outer row key to map from
:param innerRowKey: (long) - The inner row key to map to
methods.remove:
Remove a mapping from outerRowKey.

:param outerRowKey: (long) - The outer row key to unmap
:return: (long) The inner row key previously mapped from outerRowKey, or RowSequence.NULL_ROW_KEY if there was
         no mapping
methods.removeVoid:
Like WritableRowRedirection.remove(long) (long, long)}, but without requiring the implementation to provide a return value. May
 be more efficient in some cases.

:param outerRowKey: (long) - The outer row key to map from
